Her second husband Habib Ghani  28, from Hounslow, Middlesex, was killed in a gun battle in Somalia last month after falling out with senior Al Shabaab members.

He had called himself Osama al-Britani.

Lewthwaite is known to her followers as dada mzungu – Swahili for white sister.

It is claimed she has become the ‘trainer’ of an all-female suicide bomber squad targeting Westerners in East Africa.

Her appointment was announced on a website sympathetic to Al Shabaab, which revealed that Lewthwaite ‘gave her life to Allah and now she serves Allah as his female soldier in [Somalia]’, where she ‘commands her all-female mujahid terror squad and conducts operations against the kuffar [non-Muslims]’.

